Coachella Day ☝🏼 #ihavearrived #coachella2023 #musicfestivalslover #somuchfun #beckyg #fun #alldaymusic  HONEST OPINION-Day 1 : Super fun!!! Not a lot of people…no crazy lines for anything…good shows,cool people…although we always have to park wherever they want us to go and we have to walk a lot (A LOT) it was not bad!! They had the walking path wet and separated the cars,the bike rides and the people so we didn’t have sand all over our faces this year(last year was horrible,we were breathing dust,sand on the parking lot walking path) . Day 1 was very good !!!
Still Day ☝🏼 FUN !! #gorillaz #badbunny ♥️🎉 So much fun !!! Not too crazy…more details on first post 😊 #coachella #day1 #somuchfun #musicfestivalslover #mivida #amomuito

Day ✌🏼Coachella 🎉🎼🎶🎵 #fun but they started losing it! Cops and staff don’t really know what they are doing…so blocking streets and traffic started to suck!!! A lot more people than Friday…more lines,sometimes long lines to get food or anything…still fun though…😊🎉 #day2 #musicfestivalslover #thatsme #celebratelifeeveryday #charlixcx #coachella

Day ✌🏼☝🏼 #fun but a total #shitshow They (the city and staff and cops) totally lost control!! Traffic was horrible,they opened up more parking too late,they were totally not organized!! Sad!! Such a cool festival,good vibes …but they need to be prepared… I still had the best time…because I LOVE music festivals….but come on Coachella 😝😩🎵🎶🎼🎉
